## Radius, Shadows, Borders

**Radius:** sm=6px, md=8px, lg=12px, xl=16px, full=9999px

**Shadows:**
- xs: 0 1px 2px rgba(16,24,40,0.05)
- sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(16,24,40,0.1), 0 1px 2px rgba(16,24,40,0.06)
- md: 0 4px 8px -2px rgba(16,24,40,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(16,24,40,0.06)
- lg: 0 12px 16px -4px rgba(16,24,40,0.08), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(16,24,40,0.03)

**Borders:** Default = 1px solid gray-200. Inputs = 1px solid gray-300. Focus = brand-300 with 4px ring of brand-100. Error = error-300 with 4px ring of error-100.

